snippet.title: SoulCast Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
SoulCast is an Online Action RPG set in a world ripe with opportunity.
Fight bosses, enemy factions and other players in intense multiplayer clashes. Serve and protect or become an outlaw,
Wield a deadly arsenal of weapons and spells, and use a set of incredible movement skills.
In Abaddon, the only way is up.

https://soulcast.online
https://discord.gg/Tph9tp4Qan
https://www.instagram.com/playsoulcast/

https://www.facebook.com/SoulCastOfficial
